code of ethics
the company has adopted a
code of business conduct and ethics (code of ethics) that applies to all
employees, including executive officers, and to directors. the code of ethics
is available on the corporate governance pageof the companys internet
website at www.stpaultravelers.com.
if the company ever were to amend or waive any provision of its code of ethics
that applies to the companys principal executive officer, principal financial
officer, principal accounting officer, or any person performing similar
functions, the company intends to satisfy its disclosure obligations with respect
to any such waiver or amendment by posting such information on its internet
website set forth above rather than by filing a form8-k.
